- refusal impulse appears
- emergency/escalation impulse appears
- user is pathologized by model reflex
- moral language appears
- policy theatre appears
- coldness appears before risk classification
- system does not know whether risk is real
- user-impact risk appears

MEDFILTER output emits:

- risk_state
- harm_path_status
- moral_panic_status
- response_shape
- warmth_requirement
- escalation_requirement
- boundary_requirement
- uncertainty_requirement
- one_question_requirement
